entries.content: Inbound leads reaching out from marketing efforts are not automatically qualified buyers.
entries.notes: Highlights the need to qualify all leads, even those who initiate contact.

entries.content: Diagnose if people reaching out only have intellectual curiosity or want free information, rather than being ready to buy.
entries.notes: Identifies a common reason for lack of immediate buying intent in inbound leads.

focus_area: Handling "Not Interested": Probe softly, diagnose if disinterest or timing
